description.en:
WaterDrop is a native token of Decentralized Exchange called ""WATER"" which will be launched by 2021. 
Waterdrop token is Decentralized token On Ethereum Block Chain. Waterdrop can be used to stake, Buy, Sell Digital Products like Digital Marketing, Web services, and more. WDP can be traded/exchange with cryptocurrencies (Bitcoin, ETH, waves, USDT and ETC).
